reviewText: I got exactly the item that i ordered in a timely fashion and was very satisfied with the item i received. Def comedy jam Allstars 13.
I love Mark Curry. He danced and was too crazy funny. You will play this one over and over for certain.
Purchased this for my DVD Collection. I'm into comedy and comedians. I can sit around (if I had the time) and watch comedians all day long. Good for a great laugh.
